{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act26side_level_act26side_07_end","storyGroup":"act26side","storySort":16,"storyDependence":"act26side_level_act26side_07_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"HE-7","storyName":"以爱相连","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"最后的圣餐已经开始，费德里科鸣铳打断众人争执，拉特兰诸人各自行动。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act26side/level_act26side_07_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act26side_07","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":14,"next":16,"characters":["约里","修道院主教","胆怯的萨卡兹居民","蕾缪安","奥伦","斯普莉雅","费德里科","？？？","里凯莱"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8e/Avg_bg_39_g7_chapel.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":7},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":8},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","id":9},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"skz1","loop":"false","delay":"0.6","id":10},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"skt1","loop":"false","delay":"2.6","id":11},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_walk_stage","channel":"skt2","loop":"false","delay":"3.2","id":12},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":13},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_932_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":15},{"type":"charslot","id":16},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_938_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":17},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_189","duration":"1","id":18},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":19},{"type":"charslot","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_runstop","volume":"0.8","id":22},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_939_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_939_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"约里","text":"早安，主教阁下。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_939_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"早安，又见面了，约里。请招呼一下其他人。","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_939_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"约里","text":"好的。","id":30,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/2/21/Avg_avg_npc_939_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的萨卡兹居民","text":"主教阁下，我们......","id":32,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"最近发生了很多事，苏拉尔，我理解你的愁苦。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_934_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"胆怯的萨卡兹居民","text":"我们是不是不该来？拉特兰来的那些人会不会......","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d9/Avg_avg_npc_934_1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_923_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"没关系。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"生活在安布罗修修道院的人，都有资格进入礼拜堂，十年来都是如此。","id":39,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"就坐在第一排吧，苏拉尔，像以前一样，不用紧张。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"拉特兰人不会打扰已经开始的圣餐仪式。","id":41,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/02/Avg_avg_npc_923_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":43},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"charslot","id":46},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":48},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","volume":"0.1","loop":"true","channel":"crwd","id":49},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"各位，请入座。","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"接下来是餐前祷告的时间。请各位等待，请各位聆听，请各位感受此刻的宁静。","id":53},{"type":"dialog","id":54},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"crwd","fadetime":"3","id":55},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialog","id":57},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":58},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":59},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_39_i09.png","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.7","yScale":"1.7","x":"450","y":"100","fadetime":"0","id":60},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.7","yScaleFrom":"1.7","xScaleTo":"1.7","yScaleTo":"1.7","xTo":"380","yTo":"60","duration":"15","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":62},{"type":"playmusic","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/avg/m_avg_monastery_nomal.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":63,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":64},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"本人斯特凡诺·托雷格罗萨，安布罗修修道院主教，向各位居民致意。","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我习惯用“居民”来称呼大家，而非“信徒”“同胞”或者其他。","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"世人，包括我们自己，对萨科塔和萨卡兹的印象从来如此，律法与野蛮、秩序与暴力、和平与战争、天使与恶魔云云......","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"光环与角是我们醒目的体貌，是镌刻进生命的符号，我们各自都是行走在这片大地上会引来关注的群体。","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"但过去的数千个日子里，我们共同生活，今天又聚集于此，分领圣餐，共享荫护与赐福。","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"大家来到修道院的时间有长有短，但最短的也已逾十年。","id":71},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"在更长的时间里，我们无从确定自己是否已遭离弃，或已被遗忘。我们未知前路，而又身处险地，终于在无人知晓的歧路相逢。","id":72},{"type":"dialog","id":73},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_39_i09.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"2","xScale":"1.7","yScale":"1.7","x":"-450","y":"100","id":74},{"type":"imagetween","image":"39_i09","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.7","yScaleFrom":"1.7","xScaleTo":"1.7","yScaleTo":"1.7","xTo":"-380","yTo":"60","duration":"15","id":75},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我们并非没有矛盾，我们并非没有隐秘，但我们试着彼此接纳。","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"此刻，礼拜堂中的所有人，我们知晓对方的名姓，了解彼此的习惯，我们自觉分享食物，愿意为对方抵御风雨。","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我们共同驱赶野兽，对抗匪徒；我们共同烧制砖石，整理路面；我们修补每一扇窗户，耕种每一垄粮食。","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我们亲如手足，我们彼此爱护，我们将对方的安宁视作自己的所求。","id":80},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我们的联系如此紧密，共同的体貌或天然的感应不足以证明什么，信仰的差异或理念的分歧不足以阻隔什么。","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"但我们苦熬长夜，却禁受不住晨光熹微之时的寒冷。","id":82},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1a/Avg_39_i09.png","fadetime":"2","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","id":84},{"type":"imagetween","image":"39_i09","fadetime":"0.5","xScaleFrom":"1.","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"0.85","yScaleTo":"0.85","duration":"12","id":85},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"远道而来的拉特兰特使、执行者，以及......异域的使者，他们各有盘算，带来了新的希望，也带来了令人苦痛的抉择。","id":87},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我们本就残破的梁柱在大火中倾塌，我们可敬可靠的手足在矛盾中殒命......","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"斯特凡诺·托雷格罗萨想要谋求尽善的结果，哪怕那是一个未经验证的答案，为此我祈求各位的原谅。","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"安布罗修修道院并非乐土，但它是我们共同的“家园”。","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"我相信我们会做出一样的选择。","id":91},{"type":"dialog","id":92},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialog","id":94},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":95},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"charslot","id":97},{"type":"image","id":98},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":99},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":100},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":101},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修道院主教","text":"祷告结束，请各位领取并享用圣餐。","id":103},{"type":"dialog","id":104},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":105},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":106},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":107},{"type":"charslot","id":108},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/1d/Avg_bg_39_g8_outsidepath.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":111,"musicid":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":113},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"疼吗？","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"还好。","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"别嘴硬了，奥伦，我都听见你上下牙打颤的声音了。","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/3/32/Avg_avg_4015_spuria_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"力气再怎么大，狙击铳铳管的威力也不会大过它的子弹。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"我不介意真给你一颗。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#9$1","focus":"m","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"我能清晰感受到你的愤怒......真是强烈。","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你在为我冒犯了你信仰的纯粹而愤怒。这样的愤怒，说明你正是作为一个拉特兰人在思考问题。","id":126,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"你的任务是将安布罗修修道院带回拉特兰，救助其中意外离散的萨科塔同胞。而我的目标，则是维护拉特兰之所以为拉特兰的合理性。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"放下那些感性的念头吧，蕾缪安，我们从来都没有矛盾。","id":128,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-9$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"你依然在诡辩。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"这套靠用冠冕堂皇的大道理唬人的说辞，是从维多利亚那些公爵，还是从哥伦比亚那些商人身上学来的，万国信使奥伦？","id":131,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"我说过，突然出现的野兽会惊吓到流浪的人，我不会坐视一场屠杀发生。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"特勤部队马上就会就位，你阻拦不了我。","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_925_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":135},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"我大可以制服你，然后再想办法搞定他们。","id":136,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/e/e8/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_355_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"除非你真正对着我的脑袋给我一颗子弹，不然这样的偷袭不会成功第二次了，蕾缪安。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/d/d4/Avg_avg_npc_355_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_925_1#7$1","focus":"m","id":140},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":141},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunload","volume":"1","id":142},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"是吗？","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/4/47/Avg_avg_npc_925_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":145},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4015_spuria_1#3$1","focus":"m","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"等等，学姐，奥伦，不是吧，你们要来真的——","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/84/Avg_avg_4015_spuria_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"charslot","id":149},{"type":"playsound","key":"$pistol","volume":"0.9","id":150},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":151},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":152},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_39_i07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"0","yFrom":"0","xTo":"510","yTo":"120","xScaleFrom":"1.8","yScaleFrom":"1.8","xScaleTo":"1.8","yScaleTo":"1.8","duration":"0.1","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":157},{"type":"text","text":"突兀的一声轰鸣截断了在场三人的话头。","id":158},{"type":"dialog","id":159},{"type":"playsound","key":"$pistol","volume":"0.9","id":160},{"type":"playsound","key":"$pistol","volume":"0.9","loop":"false","channel":"shot","delay":"0.4","id":161},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"60","vibrato":"40","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":162},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":163},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.2","block":"true","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":167},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":168},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":170},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":171},{"type":"charslot","id":172},{"type":"image","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/5/50/Avg_39_i07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":174},{"type":"text","text":"来不及反应，紧接着又是同样的两声，近得让人觉得守护铳仿佛是贴在耳边发射，有那么几秒，他们甚至听不见自己的心跳声。","id":175},{"type":"text","text":"火舌在清晨湿润的空气中舔出伤口一般的长痕，天光乍破。","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunload","volume":"1","id":178},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":179},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$exciting_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_exciting02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":180,"musicid":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"false","id":181},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"拉特兰公证所执行者费德里科，鸣铳示警。","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"教皇厅枢机辅佐官蕾缪安、万国信使奥伦，还有随我同来的第六厅技术员斯普莉雅，立即停止你们无谓的争斗。","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"我没有必要理解你们的立场，更没有必要调停你们的冲突。","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"任务尚未完成，新生的变故尚有继续恶化的可能，这座异乡的修道院此刻需要秩序。","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"如果如你们所说，你们没有矛盾，却争执难断，拥有共感的群体却依旧有崩解的可能......","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"那么我来维持秩序。","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"鸣铳同样是对外面特勤部队的示警，拉特兰的官方军队决不能贸然进入安布罗修修道院。","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"奥伦，你私下调动了他们，那么就由你来负责约束。让他们后退一公里待命。","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"蕾缪安，斯普莉雅，你们此前与居住在这里的萨科塔和萨卡兹接触较多，接下来负责安抚他们的情绪，防止事态恶化。","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"完成任务后，前往礼拜堂会合。里凯莱已经发现了一些线索，正在追查。","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"而我会尽快找出这几起异常事件背后的人。","id":193},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"奥伦","text":"......","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯普莉雅","text":"......","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"......","id":198},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"费德里科","text":"现在，行动。","id":201},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":205},{"type":"image","id":206},{"type":"charslot","id":207},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":208},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_bg_39_g10_monasterycorridor_d.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":210},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":211,"musicid":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"祷告结束，请各位领取并享用圣餐。","id":214},{"type":"dialog","id":215},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":216},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":217},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#6$1","duration":"1","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":219},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#6$1","focus":"m","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"唉......紧赶慢赶，终究还是没来得及。","id":221,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/9/94/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":222},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#6$1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","duration":"0.3","id":223},{"type":"text","text":"礼拜堂的门留了一条缝，里凯莱贴过去看了看，领完无酵饼和葡萄酒的众人已经回到了座位上。","id":224},{"type":"text","text":"隔得远远的，祷告台上年迈的主教抬头看向门外，里凯莱有种和对方对视了的错觉。","id":225},{"type":"dialog","id":226},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorclosequite","volume":"1","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":228},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_gunequip","volume":"0.4","id":229},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_handcuff","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.2","id":230},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":231},{"type":"text","text":"里凯莱停顿了一秒，然后将礼拜堂的大门合紧。他想了想，又从腰间掏出一支备用铳柄将门的把手别住。","id":232},{"type":"dialog","id":233},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"差不多了，接下来就只能等里面......结束了。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":236},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"none","id":237},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":238},{"type":"playsound","key":"$pistol","volume":"0.4","id":239},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":240},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#5$1","focus":"m","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"唔？这么果断，看来是费德里科......他都遇到了情况，那这边就只剩下我一个人收尾了......","id":242,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0c/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-5$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#8$1","focus":"m","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"真麻烦啊。","id":244,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"早知道，还不如领另外那份去萨尔贡调查失踪的万国信使的任务呢，远是远了点，但那帮和黄沙打交道的家伙情感总不会这么复杂。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"难不成，我注定要成为一个工作狂？还真是应了那句不知道哪儿听来的俗语，“命不由人”。","id":246,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/8/82/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-8$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bullet_loading","id":248},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":249},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_372_1#1$1","focus":"m","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"唔，膛线与触发装置正常，守护铳随时可以使用。","id":251,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"万一里面的人待会儿都......一发一个能解决吗......子弹可能不够。难不成用拳头？","id":252,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"里凯莱","text":"等回到拉特兰，得向公证所申请一次奖励休假才行，这个工作量，不可能不给批吧。","id":253,"figure":"https://prts.wiki/images/f/fb/Avg_avg_npc_372_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":256},{"type":"charslot","id":257},{"type":"image","id":258}],"characters":["约里","修道院主教","胆怯的萨卡兹居民","蕾缪安","奥伦","斯普莉雅","费德里科","？？？","里凯莱"]}